    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>A colorless crystalline solid used industrially as a crosslinking agent to form stable alcohol gels. Dissolved in methanol or Freon and deposited on paper as an aerosol spray, has been used as a nonaqueous deacidication treatment.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
